cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is about video classification and captioning using deep neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the effectiveness of task granularity for transfer learning, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses the Something-Something dataset, which is a popular dataset in multimedia (cs.MM) research.
